the hitchhiker 's guide to the galaxy is a 2005 british-american comic science fiction film directed by garth jennings , based upon previous works in the media franchise of the same name , created by douglas adams .   it stars martin freeman , sam rockwell , mos def , zooey deschanel and the voices of stephen fry and alan rickman .   adams , who co-wrote the screenplay with karey kirkpatrick , died in 2001 , before production began ; the film is dedicated to him .   the film released to generally positive critical reaction and grossed over $ 100 million worldwide .